---
import Layout from "@halleyfante/documentation/Layout";
---

<Layout
  title="Playground"
  description="Web playground for Pix"
  current="playground"
>
  <p>
    The playground is a web editor with syntax highlighting, autocomplete,
    and a live preview canvas. Pull the Docker image and run it:
  </p>
  <pre><code>docker pull ghcr.io/halleyfante/pix/playground:latest
docker run -p 3000:3000 ghcr.io/halleyfante/pix/playground:latest</code></pre>
  <p>
    Open <code>http://localhost:3000</code> in your browser.
  </p>
  <img src="/playground.png" alt="Pix Playground showing a heart drawn with circles and a triangle on a 17x17 grid" />
</Layout>
